                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>). I was present at the Middlesex Ses<lb></lb>sions on the 21st February, and heard the prisoner convicted—I am sure he is the man—I produce the certificate of his conviction (<hi rend="italic">read</hi>).</p>
